        <mxCell id="WF0EzW6Wfc_7B3m30nf0-17" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Native Integrations are fully built into Subathon Manager.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;External Integrations are supported solely through external systems, and are processed as &quot;External&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Partial Integrations are external integrations that have partial native support, in terms of configuration and naming.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Anything with a * are missing features that are planned but currently blocked, or solved via other means.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
